slate-100 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-200 dark:hover:border-indigo-500/20 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-4 h-4\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-black\">이메일 답변</span></div></div></div><div class=\"animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top-2 duration-500\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><label class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest px-1\">연락처 <span class=\"text-indigo-600\">*</span></label><input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"010-0000-0000\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 transition-all dark:text-white\"/></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><label class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest px-1\">문의 내용 <span class=\"text-indigo-600\">*</span></label><textarea rows=\"8\" placeholder=\"내용을 상세히 입력해 주시면 더욱 정확한 답변이 가능합니다.\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 transition-all dark:text-white resize-none\"></textarea></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 p-5 bg-indigo-50/50 dark:bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100 dark:border-white/5\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-lg border-2 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer transition-all border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800\"></div><div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-2\"><span class=\"cursor-pointer select-none hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors\">개인정보 수집 및 이용에 동의합니다</span><a href=\"/privacy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-indigo-600 font-black underline decoration-indigo-200 underline-offset-4 hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors\">(상세보기)</a></div></div><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"w-full py-5 rounded-[1.5rem] font-black text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-4 transition-all shadow-2xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 text-slate-400 cursor-not-allowed border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5\">개인정보 동의가 필요합니다<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send w-5 h-5 opacity-20\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg></button></form></div><aside class=\"lg:w-80 space-y-8\"><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 space-y-8 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 pb-4 px-1\">Info</h3><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 group\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-2xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-5 h-5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">24시간 내 답변</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium\">영업일 기준 24시간 이내에 전문 상담사가 배정됩니다.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 group\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-2xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">1:1 맞춤 상담</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium\">단순 정보 전달을 넘어 최적의 해결책을 제시해 드립니다.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 group\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-2xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">개인정보 보안</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium\">입력하신 정보는 상담 목적으로만 안전하게 사용됩니다.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 space-y-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 pb-4 px-1\">Email Inquiry</h3><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 group cursor-pointer hover:border-indigo-500 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-3.5 h-3.5 text-indigo-600\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\">직접 문의</span></div><p class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 truncate\">zmetron@nate.com</p></div><p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed px-1 pt-2\">서류 첨부나 대량 문의가 필요하신 경우 위 이메일로 연락 주시면 더욱 편리합니다.</p></div></div></aside></div></main></div></div><footer class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 border-t border-border pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12\"><div class=\"footer-brand\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-lg mb-4 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-foreground\" href=\"/\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"16.785185185185185\" viewBox=\"0 0 81 61.8\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"\" id=\"vibe-logo-svg\"><path fill=\"#D7D7D7\" d=\"M30 59H20c-9 0-17-8-17-17V3s5 11 22 11S47 3 47 3v39c0 9-8 17-17 17z\"></path><path fill=\"#ef4444\" d=\"M61 59H32s5 0 10-6 5-11 5-11V3h31v39c0 9-7 17-17 17z\"></path><path fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"color:var(--foreground);transition:color 0.3s ease\" d=\"M20 62C9 62 0 53 0 42V3a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v